OL,3,C'I was totally butchered': Mum-of-four
OL,4,Cwas awake during botched Turkey surgery
OL,6,FSara Platt was left in debilitating
OL,7,Fpain, suffered shocking injuries and
OL,8,Fbecame so badly infected, a Turkish
OL,9,Fsurgeon had to operate on her while
OL,10,Fshe was awake. ITV News Reporter Ellie
OL,11,FPitt spoke to Sara and her team of NHS
OL,12,Fmedics as they prepare for her 10th
OL,13,Foperation to fix the damage.
OL,15,FSara Platt had an operation in Turkey
OL,16,Fin 2021 to reduce the size of her
OL,17,Fstomach.
