OL,3,C'I was totally butchered': Mum-of-four
OL,4,Cwas awake during botched Turkey surgery
OL,6,FShe lost 12 stone but was left with
OL,7,Fexcess skin that she said rubbed
OL,8,Ftogether, causing sores and an
OL,9,Funpleasant smell.
OL,11,FThe 33-year-old spent a year
OL,12,Fresearching her options and visited a
OL,13,FTurkish clinic before choosing which
OL,14,Fcompany to go with.
OL,16,FIn February 2023, Sara flew over to
OL,17,Fhave the skin removed as well as a
OL,18,Fbreast lift and implants.
