OL,6,FBut as soon as she woke up from the
OL,7,Fprocedure, she felt something was
OL,8,Fwrong.
OL,10,F"I remember coming round and my Dad
OL,11,Fbeing by the side of me and saying,
OL,12,F'you need to breathe Sara, you need to
OL,13,Fbreathe'," she said,
OL,15,F"There were loads of nurses around me
OL,16,Fand I was like 'kill me, tell them to
OL,17,Fkill me, Dad, you need to tell them to
OL,18,Fkill me. I can't do this, you need to
OL,19,Ftell them'."
