OL,6,FShe explained: "As he was undoing it,
OL,7,Fall this brown liquid started seeping
OL,8,Fout of my body. I screamed. I felt
OL,9,Flike I was falling apart. It was like,
OL,10,Foh my god, my insides are gonna come
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,F"It's not a health holiday. They told
OL,14,Fme I'd be sitting by the pool within
OL,15,Fthree days. I was rotting in a hotel
OL,16,Froom."
OL,18,FSara's dream of a new body had become
OL,19,Fa nightmare and was close to killing
OL,20,Fher.
