OL,3,C'I was totally butchered': Mum-of-four
OL,4,Cwas awake during botched Turkey surgery
OL,6,FAs she lay in her hotel room, her
OL,7,Fwounds were not healing, her body was
OL,8,Friddled with infection and her skin
OL,9,Ftissue was dying.
OL,11,FThe Turkish surgeon decided to perform
OL,12,Fa second procedure.
OL,14,FThis time Sara was not taken into an
OL,15,Foperating theatre but what looked like
OL,16,Fa beauty clinic
OL,18,FOnly local anaesthetic was used during
OL,19,Fthe surgery. It meant Sara was awake
OL,20,Fwhile the doctor worked on the wound
OL,21,Fin her stomach.
