OL,7,Fgiven a fit-to-fly certificate that
OL,8,Fallowed her to return home to South
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FWhen she got back, she went to A&E
OL,12,Fwhere Professor Iain Whitaker was the
OL,13,FConsultant Plastic Surgeon on call.
