OL,3,C'I was totally butchered': Mum-of-four
OL,4,Cwas awake during botched Turkey surgery
OL,6,F"Sara's was a devastating case with
OL,7,Fsignificant infection, lots of tissue
OL,8,Fthat was dead. It was life-
OL,9,Fthreatening, if there'd been a delay
OL,10,Fin hospital admission or transfer,
OL,11,Fthen there definitely would have been
OL,12,Fa chance of mortality," Professor
OL,13,FWhitaker said.
OL,15,FSara spent more than eight weeks in
OL,16,Fhospital in Wales and underwent nine
OL,17,Fsurgeries to save her life and rebuild
OL,18,Fher body.
