OL,6,FHer right breast could not be rescued
OL,7,Fand she has significant scarring,
OL,8,Fincluding a skin graft on her stomach
OL,9,Fthat attached to the muscle beneath.
OL,11,FThis is known as tethering and has
OL,12,Fbeen causing Sara excruciating pain
OL,13,Fwhile also limiting her physical
OL,14,Fmobility.
OL,16,FSara allowed ITV News to follow her as
OL,17,Fshe had her tenth corrective operation
OL,18,Ffollowing her botched surgery in
OL,19,FTurkey.
