OL,4,Cwas awake during botched Turkey surgery
OL,6,FThe mum of four said she let the
OL,7,Fcameras in because she wanted to show
OL,8,Fthe real consequences of having
OL,9,Fcosmetic procedures abroad and warn
OL,10,Fothers.
OL,12,FOn August 14 2024, Sara had surgery to
OL,13,Fremove the 8cm wide and 11cm long skin
OL,14,Fgraft. Professor Whitaker successfully
OL,15,Fclosed the gap it left and sealed her
OL,16,Fskin.
OL,18,FHe believes it will significantly
OL,19,Freduce her pain and improve her range
OL,20,Fof movement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
