OL,6,FThe British Association of Aesthetic
OL,7,FPlastic Surgeons estimates that the
OL,8,Faverage cost to the NHS to treat those
OL,9,Fwith complications from surgery abroad
OL,10,Fis #15,000 per patient.
OL,12,FProfessor Whitaker said as well as the
OL,13,Ffinancial implications, treating
OL,14,Fpatients like Sara also costs the NHS
OL,15,F"bed days where other patients could
OL,16,Fbe treated".
OL,18,F"There's no doubt we would like not to
OL,19,Fbe doing these procedures because
OL,20,Fthese were done well in the first
OL,21,Fplace," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
