OL,6,F"But I think particularly if it's
OL,7,Faffecting pain or function or the
OL,8,Fpsychological effects, people may
OL,9,Fthink it's just aesthetic and it
OL,10,Freally isn't.
OL,12,F"Whether there should be a cost that
OL,13,Fthe patient themselves pay or
OL,14,Finsurance pays or comes from overseas
OL,15,Fis, is something that is being
OL,16,Fdiscussed."
OL,18,FSara says she "cannot be more
OL,19,Fthankful" for her surgery and the care
OL,20,Fshe has received and will "repay the
OL,21,FNHS for saving my life".
